imes forced to use, right through to our cooking methods and ultimately the disposal of everything we do not need or use.<\/p>\n<p>If you have and, ideas or suggestions how you feel that <strong>Red Radish<\/strong> can improve or do more to help then please do <a title=\"email Red Radish\" href=\"mailto:wayne@red-radish.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>get in touch<\/strong><\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><a title=\"Download the Red Radish Sustainability Policy\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/02\/Red-Radish-Hospitality-and-catering-sustainability-Policy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>You can read and download our full Hospitality and Catering Sustainability and Environmental Policy.\u00a0<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>UK Festival crew catering and sustainability seem to go hand in hand these days, and as lovers of the world and parents to five children, we try to think hard&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/crew-catering-at-festivals-and-sustainability\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4479,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4477","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-latest-blog-postings"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Crew Catering at Festivals and Sustainability - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/crew-catering-at-festivals-and-sustainability\/\